data.description: PRIME REAL ESTATE! INVESTORS!! Take a look at this appx 7.78 acres (possibly 5+additional acres).  Hwy 331 South is in eye sight of this property so the opportunities and options of what you can do with this piece are endless.  Only minutes from the Sugar Sand Beaches of South Walton this property features 2 homes, one huge double wide and one single wide mobile home as well as appx 20 RV site hook ups, 7 stocked fish ponds, gazebos, decks for fishing, docks, swings for relaxing, garden area, trails and roads already put in place.  Owner is in the process of renovating a building for a general mercantile store for RV park or possibly turned into another short term rental.  Buyer to verify all info
